The following features will be added (in a timely fashion):

/quote command (for those who dont know, it means to send raw commands, so you could for instance, type "/quote toc_add_buddy someone")

have the status window display information for your current query, whether or not that person is on your buddy list

supporting adding, removing people from your buddy list

support blocking people


The following features will be added eventually:
file transfer

dcc chat

chat rooms

Things that will never be done:
bug fixes
any type of command that has malicious intent (such as some sort of flooder)
